description: [``botocore``] Added WaitForTransitioningInstances parameter to the CancelInstanceRefresh API, allowing the caller to cancel an instance refresh without waiting for on-going launches and terminations.
[``botocore``] Added a new API - DescribeAlarmContributors API, to retrieve alarm contributors in ALARM state. Added support in DescribeAlarmHistory API to query alarm contributor history
[``botocore``] SDK release for user defined predefined attributes.
[``botocore``] Added CUE tag SCTE output to MediaPackageV2 HLS and LL-HLS manifests.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for AWS Organizations APIs.

[``botocore``] Released IPv6 support with dual-stack domain options on SageMaker Studio and introduced support for p6-b200.48xlarge instance type on SageMaker Studio for JupyterLab and CodeEditor applications.
